just_use one_card_hunt.py

# label: TOOL
# role: hunt for single-card-stuck states

Random deal → tricks engine plays until stall → if hand has
exactly 1 card AND deck < 45 cards remaining, post the
state as a puzzle and stop. The tightest filter of the hunt
family — single-card-trouble is the BFS solver's sweet spot.

## Pointers

- Sibling hunts: `beginner_hunt.py`, `complex_hunt.py`,
  `deep_hunt.py`.
- Output target: random-deal corpus
  (`corpus/sessions.txt`).
